title: Space Force Col. Richard Kniseley to keynote SpaceNews 2023 Icon Awards
summary: U.S. Space Force Col. Richard Kniseley, the head of Space Systems Command’s Commercial Space Office (COMSO), will deliver the keynote address at the SpaceNews 2023 Icon Awards on Dec. 5 in Washington.

title: Space Force to begin procurement of missile-tracking satellites for medium Earth orbit constellation
summary: The U.S. Space Force is moving forward with plans to procure 27 missile-defense satellites for a medium Earth orbit constellation — using an acquisition process that mirrors the model adopted by the Space Development Agency for the military's low Earth orbit architecture.

title: Spanish propulsion startup raises seed round
